title: FEMA HAZUS, Houston-Galveston port facility to handle hazardous material affected by Hurricane Ike, USA, Sep 13 2008
name: FEMA HAZUS, Houston-Galveston port facility to handle hazardous material affected by Hurricane Ike, USA, Sep 13 2008
description:
The point shapefile shows locations of port facilities (piers etc) handling hazardous materials that may be affected by Hurricane Ike's storm surge at landfall on Sep 13 2008. 
The data was extracted from FEMA's HAZUS-MH Hurricane and Flood model.
